Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:46.91,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}加速するその痛みから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:51.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}誰かをきっと守れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:54.47,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Looking! The blitz loop this planet to search way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:58.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Only my RAILGUN can shoot it. 今すぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:04.94,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}身体中を　光の速さで　駆け巡った　確かな予感
